{
  "text": "The exact cellular mechanism of action of LEV is not completely understood, although it is known that that LEV binds selectively to SV2A [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . SV2A is expressed throughout the brain and localizes to both glutamatergic and GABAergic presynaptic terminals.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "8508493",
